pageContext.claim: “Stacey Abrams, who by the way, went down to defeat in front of a terrific gentleman from the great state of Georgia, Brian Kemp. And they came in with -- oh, they brought them all. They had President Obama, they had Michelle Obama, they had Oprah Winfrey, they came in.”
pageContext.analysis: Michelle Obama did not visit Georgia or campaign for Democratic governor candidate Stacey Abrams.
